channel.title: Alex Webber's Deep & Electro Sessions
channel.itunes:author: Alex Webber
channel.description:
This FREE Podcast is a journey through the best in deep house, electro, techno & progressive sounds on the dancefloor. Each episode will take you on a journey through house, electro, progressive, techno. Selected & Mixed by Alex Webber dj - ITALY.
Alex Webber was artistically born in the second half of the 90s. Moulded by a deep passion for electronic music after experimenting with Detroit Techno, Minimal, Experimental, Progressive, Dream and Trance he eventually found his true vocation with House music in 2000. His music and DJ sets take listeners on an eclectic journey influenced by his maverick musical background but they are built on carefully selected electro & house rhythms.
www.myspace.com/alexwebber
